Class CPDImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CPD, SF, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class CPDImpl
extends SFImpl
implements CPD
    An implementation of the model object 'CPD'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • CP Desc
    • GCGID Len
    • Num Cd Pts
    • GCSGID
    • CPGID
    • Enc Scheme
